Heat oven to 450 degrees F. Cut chicken into bite-sized pieces. Melt Saute Express(R) square in 10-inch nonstick skillet over medium-low heat just until bubbles begin to form. Add chicken. Saute 4-5 minutes or until chicken is done. Brush liquid from pan over pizza crust. Top with spinach, chicken and cheeses. Place pizza directly on oven rack. Bake 10-12 minutes or until cheese melted.